body_html: The only thing I've figured out that commenting out the call to tensorflow::ImportNumpy(); in tf_session.i:33 keeps the segfault from occurring, but then inevitably get a segfault when trying to actually do anything in TF (like call someconstant.eval()).

body: The only thing I've figured out that commenting out the call to `tensorflow::ImportNumpy();` in `tf_session.i:33` keeps the segfault from occurring, but then inevitably get a segfault when trying to actually do anything in TF (like call someconstant.eval()).
